data.description: Welcome to 1268 Knollwood Drive! Offering peace of mind, a brand new roof was installed in the spring of 2019. The interior boasts a fresh aesthetic, featuring new carpet and laminate floors, along with beautifully refinished hardwood floors in all bedrooms completed in 2015. The basement, complete with a charming fireplace, adds warmth and character to the home. Outside, a spacious fenced-in backyard with a deck and shed provides a private oasis for relaxation and entertainment. The property also includes a substantial attached 2 car garage, offering ample storage space for all your needs. What sets this home apart is its rich history; once serving as the residence for the Church Pastor, it carries a sense of community and purpose that adds a unique dimension to its charm.
